#: book/06-github/sections/3-maintaining.asc:50
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
".The repository settings link\n"
"image::images/reposettingslink.png[The repository settings link]\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: book/06-github/sections/3-maintaining.asc:55
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Then select \"`Collaborators`\" from the menu on the left-hand side.\n"
"Then, just type a username into the box, and click \"`Add collaborator.`\"\n"
"You can repeat this as many times as you like to grant access to everyone you like.\n"
"If you need to revoke access, just click the \"`X`\" on the right-hand side of their row.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: book/06-github/sections/3-maintaining.asc:58
#, no-wrap
